Vale Compiler
http://vale.dev/

Check version:
  ./valec --version

To compile a program:
  ./valec build [options] [module directory mappings]

Example:
  ./valec build --output-dir target hello=./samples/helloworld
  ./target/main

Run `./valec build --help` for the full list of build options.
Run `./valec --help` for the top-level command list.
